description.content:
⦁ Type of APIs: REST APIs  
⦁ Classification of APIs: Public APIs + Secured/Authorized APIs  
⦁ Algorithm used for authorization: Bearer access token  
⦁ API documentation format: cURL  
⦁ API documentation URL: [https://gorest.co.in/](https://gorest.co.in/)  
⦁ # of APIs developed: 4  
⦁ HTTP methods used: GET, POST, PATCH, DELETE  
⦁ How to get bearer access token: login to [https://gorest.co.in/](https://gorest.co.in/)  
⦁ Description about APIs:  
⦁ LIST USERS : This is a REST API that uses GET http method, to retrieve all the existing users from the database in a json format.  
Exp result: 200 OK ; Content-Type: application/json ; response time: 3 seconds  
⦁ CREATE USER : This is a REST API that uses POST http method, to create a new user in the database, in a json format  
Exp result: 201 Created ; Content-Type: application/json ; response time: 2 seconds  
⦁ UPDATE USER : This is a REST API that uses PATCH http method, to update an existing user in the database, in a json format  
Exp result: 200 OK ; Content-Type: application/json ; response time: 2 seconds  
⦁ DELETE USER : This is a REST API that uses DELETE http method, to delete an existing user in the database  
Exp result: 204 No Content ; empty response body ; response time: 2 seconds
